divs: sighting detailswhile travelling home from atlantic city to port jervis on the clear night\morning of 4-19-09 northbound on rte 23 i was at the intersection of rte 23 & the entrance to high point state park at about 3:30 am when i saw two extremely brilliant white round lights\strobelike over the western tree line. they appeared to be about 1-2 feet in diameter and over the trees about the same height again as the trees. i was frightened and stomped down on the gas pedal to get the hell away from whatever i was looking at. when i looked up again a few seconds later i saw only one light, but it was closer and larger. i was really moving and maneuvering down the hill to get away and when i looked up and back a third time a few seconds later it was gone. i don't know what it was that i saw, but i am hoping that someone else saw it too.
